            "answer": "<p>It depends on your shipping address because Tax and Custom fees are regulated by destination countries. Currently, the VAT is applied to some European countries and Canada.<br/><br/>- Regarding Tax: prices displayed on our website have not yet included taxes, but you will be informed of the exact tax rate during your checkout before you complete the order. The standard VAT rate in the EU is in the range of 16 – 27%. In Canada, the tax rate you will be charged depends on your province. Check more …<br/><br/></p>",
